3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the practicality of a virtual MIMO system and proposes a method to overcome performance degradation, which is a systems and control topic. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses a wireless system that involves transmitting multimedia data, which is a multimedia topic. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper discusses the complexity of codebook designs and encoding, which is a computational engineering topic.
